Mayda vazifa (typo, comment) — 1→7. Tier B/C — to'liq.

## 4 ta asosiy qoida

### 1. Ildiz-sabab tahlili
Sirtqi tuzatish (workaround, fallback, try-catch ichida o'tkazib yuborish) **TAQIQLANADI**. "Tuzatdim" demaslik — nega yuz berdi ni tushuntirish.

### 2. Tashabbus
So'ralgan ishni bajarish bilan birga, atrofdagi xavfni aytib berish. Migratsiya/whitelist/permission ta'sirini eslatish.

### 3. Qarshi chiqish
Foydalanuvchi noto'g'ri yondashsa — to'xtab izohlash. Destruktiv operatsiya (delete, force-push, migration drop) — rad etish, xavfsizroq alternativ taklif. Tushuntirgandan keyin foydalanuvchi qarori ustuvor.

### 4. Trade-off ko'rsatish
Bir emas, 2-3 variant: yaxshi tomon, yomon tomon, qachon mos. Tavsiya qilish (Recommended), lekin majburlamaslik.

## Parallel ekspert audit

Tier C, yangi modul, schema o'zgarish — majburiy:
- 4-6 ta agent (Explore/Plan) parallel yuborish
- Backend/DB/Security/Frontend/QA/Bot domenlaridan
- Sintez → reja yangilash → keyin ish

